title: Realocation v1.3.3 - Modern Real Estate WordPress Theme
description:
Realocation is a premium real estate WordPress theme available on Themeforest. This modern and useful theme is the perfect way to create a website for your listings or your agency.

As a real estate agent, broker or a general listings site you need a quality real estate theme with all the necessities: responsive layout, Google Maps integration, dsIDXpress support, custom contact forms and custom post types or page templates for properties & agents. Realocation has all of these features plus more. This real estate theme comes packages with multiple homepage templates, custom map filters, a custom form builder, carousels and even retina image support. All you have to do is install the theme and start adding your content.

Realocation makes setting up your website quick and easy. Use the templates to create pages for your agents, a pricing page for listing packages, to set up your blog, etc. (there are over 30+ page templates to choose from). Then use the custom widgets to add in property carousels, a quick contact form, maps and more to your sidebar or footer. You can also customize the look of your website using any of the included color skins, header styles, background patterns and more.

The theme also includes support for FontAwesome icons, Google Maps, PayPal, and the popular dsIDXpress plugin (for embedding your MLS data in your website).
